=The Ultimate Vow, Unknown to You=

10
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:09,780
=Episode 9=

11
00:01:10,075 --> 00:01:10,984
(Try to make His Highness unconscious.
I'll meet at the east gate)

12
00:01:10,985 --> 00:01:12,008
(of Chengguang Hall at midnight.
If successful,)

13
00:01:12,009 --> 00:01:13,482
(we can leave the capital
in three days.)

14
00:01:19,875 --> 00:01:21,035
Greetings, Your Highness.

15
00:01:36,034 --> 00:01:36,994
What's wrong?

16
00:01:44,674 --> 00:01:45,794
You were greedy again.

17
00:02:01,954 --> 00:02:03,070
All these years,

18
00:02:03,394 --> 00:02:04,795
you're still the same.

19
00:02:05,274 --> 00:02:06,875
Do you remember
that year at the bamboo hut?

20
00:02:07,075 --> 00:02:08,595
You stole the preserved fruit I hid,

21
00:02:09,234 --> 00:02:10,514
and choked just like this.

22
00:02:10,875 --> 00:02:12,395
You have no right to bring up the past.

23
00:02:27,995 --> 00:02:30,435
Your Highness. The Imperial Medical Institute
has prepared the medicine.

24
00:02:30,754 --> 00:02:33,394
It's time for your medicinal bath.
You must not delay for three days.

25
00:02:41,914 --> 00:02:42,834
Wait for me to return.

26
00:02:59,715 --> 00:03:01,114
Madam, please go quickly.

27
00:03:03,594 --> 00:03:04,394
(No.)

28
00:03:04,555 --> 00:03:05,634
(Just in case,)

29
00:03:05,955 --> 00:03:08,234
(I must make sure he can't catch up.)

30
00:03:09,235 --> 00:03:10,354
Tonight at midnight,

31
00:03:10,634 --> 00:03:12,354
I must escape this cage.

32
00:03:53,835 --> 00:03:54,715
You may leave.

33
00:03:55,435 --> 00:03:56,435
I'll wipe myself.

34
00:04:24,555 --> 00:04:25,675
With just this,

35
00:04:25,795 --> 00:04:27,074
you think you can kill me?

36
00:04:27,834 --> 00:04:29,154
It's just a pity.

37
00:04:29,355 --> 00:04:31,514
I won't let you get your wish so easily.

38
00:04:33,795 --> 00:04:35,195
If you want to kill me, then do it.

39
00:04:35,235 --> 00:04:36,355
Otherwise,

40
00:04:36,475 --> 00:04:38,435
I'll make you regret sparing my life.

41
00:04:41,314 --> 00:04:42,995
The game has only just begun.

